議之效力是否及於丙？（30分）', '[]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:26:24+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "2fb11834bf6a", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114120", "c": "106", "s": "0406", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "甲、申論題部分", "subject": "民事訴訟法", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年公務人員特種考試司法人員考試、法務部調查局調查人員考試、海岸巡防人員考試、未具擬任職務任用資格取得法官遴選資格考試", "original_question_number": "三", "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "judicial", "civil_category": "司法事務官法律事務組"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('judicial-388a63c0-moex-00015', 'judicial-388a63c0', 'judicial-388a63c0-moex-114-9b7ab1bb', 'sub-judicial-388a63c0-05', NULL, 'essay', 'A為甲法人董事長，A以甲法人名義向 A購買花瓶，雙方並「一手交錢，
